"which :guilabel:`Primary Project` they belong to. Leave the :guilabel:"
"`Domain ID` field set at *default*. You can also enter a decription for the "
"new user."
msgstr ""
"برای کاربر جدید، یک :guilabel:`DomainName`، یک :guilabel:`Username` و یک :"
